<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.2">
<l>vaḻuvoṉ ṟumillāc ceykaivā ṉavarkōṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">valippaṭ ṭumuṉin tuviṭuk kappaṭṭa</l>
<l>maḻaivan teḻunāḷ pēytumāt taṭaippa</l>
<l rend="indent">matucū taṉeṭut tumaṟit tamalai</l>
<l>yiḻavu tariyā tatōrīṟ ṟupiṭi</l>
<l rend="indent">yiḷañcī yantoṭarn tumuṭu kutaluṅ</l>
<l>kuḻavi yiṭaikkā liṭṭetirn tuporuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that was raised and upended by Madhusudana,</l>
<l rend="indent">who blocked the rains from coming and pouring for 7 days</l>
<l rend="indent">when the king of the celestials of faultless deed</l>
<l rend="indent">angrily sent [them] by way of [his] power,</l>
<l>called Govardana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the nervous [elephant], hastily grasping</l>
<l rend="indent">[her] newborn calf, placing the infant between [her] legs</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] turned to fight the young lion [that was] stalking [it],</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
